<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8">
	<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
	<title>GOLD GYM</title>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/bootstrap-4.0.0-dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/gym-css.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/gym-login.css">
</head>
<body>
	<header>
		<nav id="header-nav" class="navbar navbar-expand-lg bg-dark navbar-dark ">
			<div >
				<div class="navbar-header ">
					<div id="logo" alt="logo image" class="d-xs-none d-sm-block"></div>
				</div>
			</div>
				<div class="navbar-brand mr-auto">
					<a href="gym-main-afterlogin"><h1>GOLD GYM</h1></a>
				</div>
			

			<button type="button" class="navbar-toggler" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#target">
				<span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
				
			</button>

			<div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="target">		
				<ul id="nav-list" class="navbar-nav ml-auto">
					<li class="nav-item">
						<a class="nav-link" href="gym-aboutus">About Us</a>
					</li>
					
					<li class="nav-item">
						<a class="nav-link" href="gym-equipment">Equipments</a>
					</li>				
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div>
				<img class="profile" src="../gym-snippet/profile-pic.jpg" alt="profile pic" width="35px" height="35px">
				<div class="dropdown">
				  <button class="dropbtn" style="font-weight: bold; color: white;">Hello <%= name%>
				  	<i class="fa fa-caret-down"></i>
				  </button>
					  <div class="dropdown-content">
					    <form  action="/logout?_method=DELETE" method="POST">
							<button id="button" type="submit">Log Out</button>
						</form>
					    <a href="gym-update">Update Profile</a>
					    
					  </div>
				</div>
			</div>
			
		</nav>
	</header>

	<div class="wrapper">
         <div class="title-text">
            <div class="title login">
               Update Profile
            </div>
            
         </div>
         <div class="form-container">
            
            <div class="form-inner">
               
               <form class="signup" action="/gym-update" method="POST">
                  <div class="field">
                     <input type="text" name="firstname" placeholder="Update First Name" required>
                  </div>
                  <div class="field">
                     <input type="text" name="lastname" placeholder="Update Last Name" required>
                  </div>
                  <!-- <div class="field">
                     <input type="text" name="gender" placeholder="Enter Gender (M/F)" required>
                  </div>
                  <div class="field">
                     <input type="number" name="age" placeholder="Enter Age" required>
                  </div> -->
                  <div class="field">
                     <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Email Address" required>
                  </div>
                  <div class="field">
                     <input type="number" name="mobile" placeholder="Email Mobile Number" required>
                  </div>
                  <div class="field">
                     <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="Enter Current Password" required>
                  </div>
                  <div class="field">
                     <input type="password" name="newpass" placeholder="Enter New Password" required>
                  </div>
                  <!-- <div class="field">
                     <input type="password" name="confirmpass" placeholder="Confirm New Password" required>
                  </div> -->
                  
                  <div class="field btn">
                     <div class="btn-layer"></div>
                     <input type="submit" value="Update" >
                  </div>
                  <div class="field btn">
                     <div class="btn-layer"></div>
                     <a href="gym-update">
                     	<input type="button"  value="Cancel">
                     </a>
                  </div>
               </form>
            </div>
         </div>
      </div>

	<footer class="panel-footer">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="row">
				<section id="hours" class="col-sm-4">
					<span>Hours:</span><br>
					Sun-Thurs: 06:00am - 11:00pm<br>
					Fri: 08:00am - 08:00pm<br>
					Saturday Closed
					<hr class="d-xs-block d-sm-none">
				</section>
				<section id="address" class="col-sm-4">
					<span>Address:</span><br>
					Alwares Gladys marg<br>
					Ashar Residency<br>
					Thane (w)
					<hr class="d-xs-block d-sm-none">
				</section>
				<section id="response" class="col-sm-4">
					<p>The last three or four reps is what makes the muscle grow.</p>
					<p>Success usually comes to those who are too busy to be looking for it.</p>
				</section>
			</div>
			<div id="copyright" class="text-center">&copy; Copyright 2020</div>
		</div>
		
	</footer>

	<script src="css/bootstrap-4.0.0-dist/js/jquery-3.5.1.min.js"></script>
	<script src="css/bootstrap-4.0.0-dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>

</body>
</html>